title: Jamil's presence at rally a concern for MIC
text:
More 
MIC will inform Prime Minister Najib Abdul Razak of their concerns over the presence of a cabinet minister at the rally in support of the Syariah Courts (Criminal Jurisdiction) Act 1965. 
Party president Dr S Subramaniam, who is also the health minister, said he was not made aware of Minister in the Prime Minister Department Jamil Khir Baharom's intention to attend the rally.
